# Scoped to source/end2end-tests/daemon/Dockerfile.runner only.
# BuildKit picks up <dockerfile>.dockerignore alongside the Dockerfile
# and uses it in preference to any context-root .dockerignore.
#
# The runner image only needs the daemon e2e package and its sole
# workspace dep (@wardnet/js source). Everything else in the repo is
# noise — keep the build context small to skip the multi-second send
# step when the build is otherwise cache-hit.

*

!source/sdk/wardnet-js/
!source/end2end-tests/daemon/

**/node_modules/
**/.yarn/cache/
**/.yarn/install-state.gz
**/dist/
**/target/
**/.DS_Store
.git/
